; A journal that contains only automated (`=`) and periodic (`~`)
; transactions has no real postings to report on.  The stats command now
; correctly produces no output in this case, since it participates in the
; post filter chain rather than walking template postings attached to
; accounts during parse-time finalization.

= /^Income:/
    (Liabilities:Tithe)                   0.10

~ Monthly
    Income:Interest:Bank Interest     -$960.00
    Equity

test stats --now "2023-02-06"
end test
